body_html:
@zeshaoaaa We currently don't support building the TensorFlow library on Windows.

However, we do provide a precompiled AAR download that should work in your case if you set the build type in build.gradel to none. This will remove the need to build native .so libraries locally.

body:
@zeshaoaaa We currently don't support building the TensorFlow library on Windows. 

However, we do provide a precompiled AAR download that should work in your case if you set the build type in build.gradel to `none`. This will remove the need to build native .so libraries locally.
